{"tid":1839562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一眾公會立刻籌備三罷支援醫護界！","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T15:02:34.000Z","uid":120308,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9371eff66886d1c73bd0a2cf00c05ae6da2144","tid":1839562,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"之前科左水咁耐，又吹哂大雞叫人入工會，就係為左發動三罷。<br />\n<br />\n而家就係最好時間罷工，當全世界都支持醫護界，我唔明點解仲未有工會有任何行動？<br />\n<br />\n醫護界就講左有工業行動啦，其他工會呢？當醫護界condom呀？只係講咩抗疫5大訴求，有用就唔洗搞到咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n我而家同你地講，你地唔配合醫護界一齊發起工業行動，我立刻退會！<br />\n<br />\n支援醫護 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"fd3729c8f6c855704742b05ada9bbd70a97eeeae","tid":1839562,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:11:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工必須預演 刻不容緩 <br />\n<br />\n以而家既上升趨勢 點可能仲等到過完年先罷?<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工唔單止係阻止疫情<br />\n<br />\n要順勢爭取五大訴求, 唔好忘記:<br />\n<br />\n被捕 被自殺 被斬既手足<br />\n<br />\n仲等28號? 一定要預演, 否則會同1111一樣 即係西灣河槍殺人當日呀<br />\n<br />\n唔預演一陣到正日 得勁少人罷 雷聲大雨點小<br />\n<br />\n到時感染人數一定DOUBLE左<br />\n<br />\n剩係呢幾日都有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n另外再望下D相, 而家有籌碼都唔利用, 等幾時?<br />\n<br />\n仲想幾多手足死傷呀?<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3j5yZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3j5yZP.png&h=a6e38b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpcfbMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpcfbMu.jpg&h=7b2bceb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hzi2Bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzi2Bda.jpg&h=e58944e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sDJ46w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sDJ46w.jpg&h=e0d1403c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgyBFES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%